{"word":"ὅταν","slug":"ὅταν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὅταν</el></b> [for <el>ὅτ</el>’ <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄν\">ἄν</a></el> = <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅτε\">ὅτε</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄν\">ἄν</a></el>] temporal marker<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> sense, <b>when(ever) <a href='B:470 5:11'>Mt 5:11</a>; <a href='B:470 6:2'>6:2</a>; <a href='B:480 4:15'>Mk 4:15</a>; <a href='B:490 11:34'>Lk 11:34</a>; <a href='B:500 2:10'>J 2:10</a>; <a href='B:500 9:5'>9:5</a></b> (‘as long as’); <b><a href='B:540 12:10'>2 Cor 12:10</a>; <a href='B:660 1:2'>Js 1:2</a>; <a href='B:690 5:2'>1 J 5:2</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> specifically of time at which an event is anticipated, <b>when <a href='B:470 9:15'>Mt 9:15</a>; <a href='B:480 8:38'>Mk 8:38</a>; <a href='B:490 5:35'>Lk 5:35</a>; <a href='B:500 4:25'>J 4:25</a>; <a href='B:510 23:35'>Ac 23:35</a>; <a href='B:520 11:27'>Ro 11:27</a>; <a href='B:530 13:10'>1 Cor 13:10</a>; <a href='B:730 4:9'>Rv 4:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀσφύς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὅτε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}